Sky Sports pundit Gary Neville has laid into referee Lee Mason after he failed to award Newcastle a penalty during their 2-0 defeat at Liverpool on Monday night .
An incident in the 38th minute of the game , saw Ayoze Perez felled by a reckless challenge from Dejan Lovren .
Sky Sports pund Sports Gary Neville could not believe that a spot kick was not awarded to the Magpies at Anfield .